    "name": "Nekra Damage",
    "profile": "Doom | Techno | Industrial Hardcore Dj & Producer based in Nice, France.\r\n\r\nOriginally from France, Nekra Damage has been developing a distinctive sound at the crossroads of industrial, rave/hardcore techno, and EBM for over two decades, creating cinematic soundscapes with dystopian undertones.\r\nBorn in the early 2000s, the project draws its roots from the influence of Kraftwerk, DAF, Planet Core Production label, Punk and the oldschool Industrial / Hardcore Techno scene. Over the years, this approach has evolved toward a crossover of musical styles enriched with meticulous sound design work, sculpting immersive universes where techno and hardcore power meets sophisticated industrial textures.\r\nThe project performs as DJ sets or live acts in clubs, A/V festivals, and artistic events, having notably played in Berlin, Rome, Geneva, Lyon, Marseille, Cannes..\r\nIn 2019, Nekra Damage founded Culture of Violence, a label dedicated to emerging artists from the experimental electronic, industri",
